<P>Now a few years later my guild have broken up and im playing a new char (paladin) due to shedule i dont really have any interestign raid options so im forced to do what i can do in 1 group encounters to gear up and the loot from mpg trials are so good that i repeated the fear trial 13 times to get the neck.</P>
<P>Prathun finally how good gear should you be able to get in non raid encounters ? </P>
<P>The MPG 1 group trials was the hardest 1 group content in OoW and Overlord Mata Muran the hardest raid encounter in same expansion and the trial loot is around 50-60 % of what drops from OMM.</P>
<P>I dont think that is "unfair" considering how hard those trials used to be. (and btw the spell drops from mpg 1 group trials are VERY rare, or ive been VERY unlucky).</P>
<P>And about the MPG trials yes its the carrot hanging in front of you who let you go through the grueling time to get it <img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-happy.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0></P>
