<P>I completed all on my main and didnt loot a single piece, after that ive done all on my alt now and quite a few pieces was all from good to small upgrades but the trials was also far harder, in severel of them i had to ask friends for help becosue i was not able to tank them.</P>
<P>What i really miss is&nbsp;a way for people who arent able to raid&nbsp;to have a chance to get gear without having to resort to sitting in a corner of a zone pulling a ph constantly and hope someone dont run by and KS&nbsp;the named when he finally pop).</P>
